{"word":"ἀνήκουστος","slug":"ἀνήκουστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνήκουστος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀκούω'><el>ἀκούω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>unheard of</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>inauditus</el>, <el>ἤκουσ' ἀνήκουστα</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>not willing to hear</i>: <el>τὸ ἀνήκουστον</el> <i>disobedience</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}